name: UltrM
description:
This is my custom model merged with protogen infinity. It is a 360 model. It can generate almost any image that top models can generate, also support lexcia art. You can try other models prompt or your own for testing and let me know in the comment.

VAE Required: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.ckpt
